Package com.example.cs309android.models.USDA.queries

Class FoodsCriteria

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.cs309android.models.api.request.abstraction.Request
      • com.example.cs309android.models.api.request.abstraction.GetRequest
        • com.example.cs309android.models.USDA.queries.FoodsCriteria
  • public class FoodsCriteria
extends GetRequest
    JSON for request body of 'foods' POST request. Retrieves a list of food items by a list of up to 20 FDC IDs. Optional format and nutrients can be specified. Invalid FDC ID's or ones that are not found are omitted and an empty set is returned if there are no matches.

    From https://app.swaggerhub.com/apis/fdcnal/food-data_central_api/1.0.1#/FoodsCriteria

    Author:
    Mitch Hudson
